title: #92Noon Super Bowl Stories - Steve Hutchinson
description: Steve was eventually an All-Pro guard for the Vikings, but was an All-Pro guard for the Seahawks before that and played in SBXL with the Seahawks. His Hawks fell short against the the Steelers, but Hutch talks about all it with PA #92Noon!
